# 🧠 Golang Monorepo Service — Server & Worker

![Go Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/Go-1.20%2B-blue)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-green)
![Docker Support](https://img.shields.io/badge/Docker-Supported-blue)

A monorepo Go service that includes:

- 🌐 `cmd/server`: the HTTP/WebSocket API server  
- ⚙️ `cmd/worker`: the background job processor (e.g., message queue consumer)

